name: Park Avenue
description: Perfection in necklace form, this piece combines purple and fire-y red stones broken up with clear mini jewels to create the prettiest of networks. Throw over an LBD or jeans and t-shirt combo to be this year's 'Best Dressed' at the christmas party.

name: Highgate
description: Purple and green should always be seen.. especially with these coloured gems in a stunning laurel-like arrangement.

name: Waldorf
description: Living up to it's namesake, the Waldorf is the perfect mix of high fashion glamour and regality. An unexpected mix of interlocking mint stones really pop against an elegant row of amber jewels.

name: Buckingham
description: Enticing and exotic, this necklace flaunts a cool combo of emerald gems as well as a slick golden finish for a vintage look that’s truly unique.

name: Hampstead
description: Bold meets beautiful in this knockout statement necklace. With its outrageously gorgeous jewel clusters and subtle egyptian inspiration, it's a complete head-turner.

name: Shoreditch
description:
A firm favourite in the Bijoux Bazaar office, this absolutely dreamy colour combination in a mix of interlinked shapes makes for the perfect pair. 

The must have LBD accessory. 

*Please note that the colours in these earrings are ever so slightly more muted that this image.

name: Skyline
description:
Make a stunning, singular statement with this bib that features
a bevy of turquoise and amber gems we’re sure any jewel loving magpie would love.

name: Hudson
description: This petal stunner is truly a piece you are going to  treasure, featuring girly hues with a little bit of edge, the look is spectacular and serene  all at once.

name: City Cuff
description: Lovingly embellished with clear gems, this translucent cuff packs a punch in the style stakes. Perfectly stackable.

name: Uptown
description: Tortoise shell blocks, sandwiched between canary and pastel blue coloured stones make for the perfect statement pair. Pure glam.

name: Bryant Bloom
description: Just in time for winter, this blooming beauty flaunts an appealing floral motif that comes with a little bit of edge thanks to cool hematite metal work and canary yellow stones.

name: Brooklyn
description: With its grand cluster of over-sized ice-white crystals sandwiched between hardened metal links, the Brooklyn bib is just waiting for a splash of colour, courtesy of the punchiest ensemble you can dream up.

name: Hoxton Mint
description:
These stunning cocktail earrings manage to be both delicate and oh-so-bold. We're especially in love with the way those mint gems are partnered with even more dazzling crystal finery.

Available in a variety of colours

description:

Available in a variety of colours

name: Hoxton Peach
description:

name: Apfel Drops
description:
Gorgeous emerald and amber-hued topaz gems pop when framed by an array of colorful gemstones for a look that truly stands out.

Drop: 4.7cm

name: Acid Avenue Drops
description: Our affinity for neon gems reaches a new level with these daringly gorgeous drops, featuring a punchy chartreuse palette set against cool, crisp golden metal for an extra kick.

name: Soho Drop
description: These earrings are a pair of bewitching beauties, thanks to an unexpected mix of a pastel centre stone and frosty blue gems.

name: Liberty
description: These plume drops are oh-so decadent; crafted from dueling shades of amber and blue crystals the look is pure getaway glam.

name: Metropolitan
description: This hardened style is unexpectedly femme. Boasting spikey crystal accents, the finishing touches only serve to make this spectacular colour palette pop.

name: Belsize
description: This cool crystal burst pendant combines the unexpected look of snow white opaque and peach gems with a watery blue sapphire centre stone.

name: Uptown Girl
description: The girlyer sister of the original tortoise shell Uptown, this bubble gum pink centre piece anchored by a fan of clear crystals and shades of purple make these earrings a fun staple needed in every wardrobe!

name: Manhattan Neon
description:
Neon yellow oval stones housed between nests of clear crystals ensures this spectacular piece provides the most stellar contribution to any outfit. One of our most exciting pieces yet.

Also available in grey

name: Belgravia Necklace
description: Emerald centre stones encased in a network of powder blue, onyx black and clear jewels ensures this neck piece lives up to it's first class namesake.

name: Bayswater Canary
description: This stunning bracelet takes its design cues from the exotic and perfumed city of Marrakech. It's hand stitched and embellished, and totally stackable!

description:
This stunning bracelet takes its design cues from the exotic and perfumed city of Marrakech. It's hand stitched and embellished, and totally stackable!

description:

name: Ealing
description: A chic alternative to the earring, the Ealing ear cuff adds a touch of modernity to any ensemble.

name: Manhattan
description:
Light grey oval stones housed between nests of clear crystals ensures this spectacular piece provides the most stellar contribution to any outfit. One of our most exciting pieces yet.

Also available in neon yellow.

name: Chrysler
description: Pastel gems, with their ethereal dreamlike quality, are the  perfect match to worn out golden hard wear. Pops of khaki and rustic red make this the perfect piece to take you from day to night.

name: Tribeca
description: A layered melange of both coloured and clear stones makes our Tribeca the go-to piece for contemporary elegance.

name: Long Island
description: Crafted from oversized tortoise quad links and embellished with an over-the-top crystal teardrop pendant the look is totally regal, totally chic.

name: Hampton
description: Art deco is the name of the game when it comes this bold bib. Constructed from gems arranged in an intricately cut design, this look will take any outfit to the next level.

name: Bloomingdale
description:
Make them say “ooh la la” with just the flick of the wrist with
this gorgeous bracelet, covered in an array of mouth-watering crystals. An adjustable fastening ensures the perfect fit.

name: Belgravia Bracelet
description: A fantastically unexpected palette of powder blue, emerald and onyx are just the beginning with this gorgeous bracelet; oversized emerald gems and a healthy dose of pave crystals are what really make this beauty such a stunner.

name: Fulham
description:
Canary yellow and charcoal jewels built upon a white canvas. The perfect outfit update. 

As worn by Rosie Fortescue of Made in Chelsea.

name: Hoxton Blush
description:
These stunning cocktail earrings manage to be both delicate and oh-so-bold. We're especially in love with the way those blush pink gems are partnered with even more dazzling crystal finery.

Also comes in mint green.

name: Dalston
description: Double up and go for gold with this spike and diamante necklace, featuring a bevy of neon tassels.

name: Carnaby
description: A perfect network of coloured stones, the Carnaby would look equally at home dressing up a plain tee as it would around the neck of the chicest party dress.

name: City Clusters
description: Luxe onyx gems have a dark, vampy appeal, and when paired with bright jewel tones the look is truly stunning.

name: Shoreditch Green
description: A firm favourite in the Bijoux Bazaar office, the absolutely dreamy colour combination of green, onyx and slate in a mix of interlinked shapes makes for the perfect pair.

name: Brent Bug
description: A golden bug sandwiched between a pale pink drop and emerald stud makes this pair perfect for those looking to make a softer statement.
